{"tid":127232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube 明年將移除 30 秒強制廣告","createTime":"2017-02-20T03:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T09:06:54.000Z","uid":47714,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be7a2fd547da9c2ce33d715a2e332135d0c417fc","tid":127232,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://unwire.hk/2017/02/19/youtube-removes-30sec-ad/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2Fyoutube-removes-30sec-ad%2Fsoftware%2F&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e1e9e881\" target=\"_blank\">http://unwire.hk/2017/02/19/youtube-removes-30sec-ad/software/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Screen_Shot_2017_02_17_at_11.09.38_AM.0-1280x854.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FScreen_Shot_2017_02_17_at_11.09.38_AM.0-1280x854.png&h=3b8fd744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYouTube 的影片在播放之前，有時會強制加入廣告需要看完才可以收看原先選擇的影片，其中最長的廣告可達 30 秒，令人相當不耐煩。Google 最近公佈，明年將會停止這個格式。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 表示，在 2018 年他們將不會再在影片前加入 30 秒的強制廣告，集中資源在對觀衆和廣告商更加吸引的廣告格式上。當然，今次的改變只會影響 30 秒長度的廣告，15 秒和 20 秒的廣告，以及 6 秒的長方形小廣告也會繼續存在，未來也可能加入其他的廣告格式。<br />\n<br />\n今次的改動，大概是聽取了用家的意見和投訴，始終 30 秒的強制廣告也許太長，失去廣告的作用，而用家的觀賞體驗也會因此而下降。無論如何，這個改動要等到 2018 年才會實行，所以如果仍然看到 30 秒鐘的廣告，大家就先忍耐一下吧。"},{"pid":"11c3c9fa5ee44969f8daef42d95b425d2d041b65","tid":127232,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:10:41.000Z","msg":"屌你仲要等下年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ad4706e4696ef31554d10f78f0721be26f91eb","tid":127232,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"一見到超過6秒既廣告，即刻關左段片再開仲快"},{"pid":"6021ac1d9704f4